New Install:

1. Download and unzip the latest version of Bosc.
2. Put the 'bosc' directory anywhere you'd like it to be.
3. Include 'bosc/src/bosc.inc.php' from any page that you want to have access to the Bosc classes.

Upgrade:

1. Delete 'bosc' directory.
2. Follow New Install instructions.


That's it!
